WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.330
Good morning, family. How are you all

00:00:02.340 --> 00:00:04.910
doing? I have a word for you all again

00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:07.190
today; it is basically direction for

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:09.350
what the Lord has told me to tell

00:00:09.350 --> 00:00:09.360
you.

00:00:09.360 --> 00:00:13.490
I was out mowing the grass on

00:00:13.500 --> 00:00:16.250
Sunday

00:00:16.260 --> 00:00:17.930
and the Lord

00:00:17.940 --> 00:00:19.609
spoke to me about things. It was about

00:00:19.619 --> 00:00:22.790
the video that I posted on Sunday

00:00:22.790 --> 00:00:22.800
regarding

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:25.310
the great

00:00:25.320 --> 00:00:27.410
refiner's fire that was coming.

00:00:27.420 --> 00:00:29.509
People are asking me when this is going

00:00:29.519 --> 00:00:33.170
to happen and when these events are going

00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:35.330
to take place. The more I do these

00:00:35.340 --> 00:00:38.450
videos and the more I have been praying

00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:41.450
and being obedient to what He has asked me

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:43.850
to do by coming on YouTube and telling

00:00:43.860 --> 00:00:46.790
you all things, the gift

00:00:46.790 --> 00:00:46.800
is

00:00:46.800 --> 00:00:49.069
multiplying.

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:51.529
The ability to hear Him and to

00:00:51.539 --> 00:00:53.569
flow with Him in the spirit

00:00:53.579 --> 00:00:55.970
is on another level that I was

00:00:55.970 --> 00:00:55.980
not

00:00:55.980 --> 00:01:00.170
familiar with. I would

00:01:00.180 --> 00:01:02.689
see things before, and the Lord would show me

00:01:02.699 --> 00:01:06.109
things in advance, but now whenever I

00:01:06.119 --> 00:01:08.270
talk to Him, it is almost like downloads

00:01:08.280 --> 00:01:10.730
on a daily basis. I have these

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:13.010
conversations and the Lord

00:01:13.010 --> 00:01:13.020
talks

00:01:13.020 --> 00:01:16.250
to me, and it has been really

00:01:16.260 --> 00:01:19.910
different. Even my

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:21.770
prayer time is different. I was asking

00:01:21.780 --> 00:01:23.090
Him,

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:26.030
'Lord, what about all these people talking

00:01:26.040 --> 00:01:28.609
about the virus coming in the fall?'There

00:01:28.609 --> 00:01:28.619
are

00:01:28.619 --> 00:01:31.249
a lot of

00:01:31.259 --> 00:01:33.770
rumors; I see it even on InfoWars and

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:35.990
some of these other platforms.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:37.730
People were sending me

00:01:37.730 --> 00:01:37.740
stuff—my

00:01:37.740 --> 00:01:39.890
family here sends me stuff

00:01:39.900 --> 00:01:42.289
through my email telling me to watch this

00:01:42.299 --> 00:01:44.149
and that—so

00:01:44.149 --> 00:01:44.159
everybody is

00:01:44.159 --> 00:01:45.950
trying to keep me informed on

00:01:45.950 --> 00:01:45.960
what is

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:48.170
going on in the world. I

00:01:48.180 --> 00:01:50.030
appreciate everybody trying to help. I

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:50.040
cannot

00:01:50.040 --> 00:01:52.310
watch it all, but

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:54.109
the ones that my wife

00:01:54.119 --> 00:01:55.490
brings to me and says, 'I really

00:01:55.500 --> 00:01:56.990
think you should watch this one,'I

00:01:56.990 --> 00:01:57.000
will

00:01:57.000 --> 00:01:58.429
take the time to try to watch it. It

00:01:58.429 --> 00:01:58.439
has

00:01:58.439 --> 00:02:00.710
been amazing—the people, the support,

00:02:00.720 --> 00:02:02.870
and everything—with everybody all trying

00:02:02.880 --> 00:02:04.969
to be like a family. That

00:02:04.969 --> 00:02:04.979
is

00:02:04.979 --> 00:02:06.469
why I felt, whenever I was praying about

00:02:06.469 --> 00:02:06.479
what to

00:02:06.479 --> 00:02:09.109
say to you all,

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:11.809
a family connection. I want to

00:02:11.819 --> 00:02:15.050
bring us together and knit us

00:02:15.060 --> 00:02:18.410
together like a family so that

00:02:18.410 --> 00:02:18.420
we are

00:02:18.420 --> 00:02:21.229
able to lean on each other in the

00:02:21.239 --> 00:02:23.690
comment section and pray and agree

00:02:23.700 --> 00:02:25.190
with each other when we are having hard

00:02:25.200 --> 00:02:28.030
times. I see a lot of you

00:02:28.040 --> 00:02:31.430
polished Christians who really know

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:33.650
the Word come out whenever there

00:02:33.650 --> 00:02:33.660
is

00:02:33.660 --> 00:02:36.050
a person who is not as polished

00:02:36.050 --> 00:02:36.060
or

00:02:36.060 --> 00:02:39.530
a baby Christian who is asking for help,

00:02:39.540 --> 00:02:41.869
and you are just

00:02:41.879 --> 00:02:44.449
helping them. There are a lot of good,

00:02:44.459 --> 00:02:47.509
seasoned believers on this

00:02:47.519 --> 00:02:49.430
channel that are following me, and I

00:02:49.430 --> 00:02:49.440
am

00:02:49.440 --> 00:02:51.530
honored that you all are here,

00:02:51.540 --> 00:02:53.270
that we are all a family

00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:55.250
praying together. I just

00:02:55.260 --> 00:02:56.990
want to say thank you

00:02:57.000 --> 00:02:59.809
for the support. When I was

00:02:59.819 --> 00:03:02.390
praying over

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:05.390
the fall and looking

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:06.890
into the

00:03:06.900 --> 00:03:09.470
spirit, asking about it,

00:03:09.480 --> 00:03:11.509
whenever I try to tell you all what

00:03:11.509 --> 00:03:11.519
I am

00:03:11.519 --> 00:03:13.430
seeing and

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:15.710
feeling, it is like a

00:03:15.710 --> 00:03:15.720
pulse—like

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:17.330
a heartbeat on those

00:03:17.340 --> 00:03:19.729
monitors. Whenever I

00:03:19.729 --> 00:03:19.739
am

00:03:19.739 --> 00:03:22.009
praying over it, yes, there is something

00:03:22.019 --> 00:03:25.009
there about it. I asked the

00:03:25.019 --> 00:03:29.809
Lord, 'Is this a major event?'and He

00:03:29.819 --> 00:03:32.509
says it will try to be if they are going

00:03:32.519 --> 00:03:34.790
to try to make it that way. They are going

00:03:34.800 --> 00:03:38.330
to try to escalate that and fear. I am

00:03:38.330 --> 00:03:38.340
going to

00:03:38.340 --> 00:03:40.550
say it like this: Is this

00:03:40.560 --> 00:03:44.869
the 350 million that I saw? No.

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:47.449
A lot of you will not like what I

00:03:47.449 --> 00:03:47.459
am going to

00:03:47.459 --> 00:03:50.030
say, but that is years down

00:03:50.040 --> 00:03:52.430
the road. I believe, whenever I am praying,

00:03:52.430 --> 00:03:52.440
2025

00:03:52.440 --> 00:03:56.509
has the potential

00:03:56.519 --> 00:04:00.410
to be very dark. We have authority to

00:04:00.420 --> 00:04:02.630
pray over this stuff. When I am praying

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:05.330
over the virus, I saw

00:04:05.340 --> 00:04:08.089
blue states—and if you are familiar with

00:04:08.099 --> 00:04:10.490
America, the Democrats are blue and the

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:12.770
Republicans are

00:04:12.770 --> 00:04:12.780
red—you

00:04:12.780 --> 00:04:14.330
have the conservatives and the liberals.

00:04:14.330 --> 00:04:14.340
In

00:04:14.340 --> 00:04:19.310
the

00:04:19.310 --> 00:04:19.320
Democratic-run

00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:25.909
states, I saw more of an escalation in

00:04:25.919 --> 00:04:29.390
those

00:04:29.390 --> 00:04:29.400
government-run

00:04:29.400 --> 00:04:33.290
areas, escalating even more so than in

00:04:33.300 --> 00:04:36.469
the red states. Then He showed me

00:04:36.479 --> 00:04:40.129
more of a migration of people leaving

00:04:40.139 --> 00:04:43.850
the blue states, like believers that are

00:04:43.860 --> 00:04:46.010
