00:04:48.050 --> 00:04:48.060
masks,

00:04:48.060 --> 00:04:49.790
things like that.

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:51.290
I have to be careful because I do

00:04:51.290 --> 00:04:51.300
not

00:04:51.300 --> 00:04:52.730
know how far I can say some of this

00:04:52.740 --> 00:04:55.129
on here because they

00:04:55.139 --> 00:04:56.570
want to try to suppress my

00:04:56.580 --> 00:04:59.030
stuff; that is what they are trying to do

00:04:59.030 --> 00:04:59.040
