00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:09.050
I saw a

00:05:09.060 --> 00:05:11.510
migration

00:05:11.510 --> 00:05:11.520
where

00:05:11.520 --> 00:05:12.969
people

00:05:12.969 --> 00:05:12.979
