00:05:12.979 --> 00:05:16.310
relocating more and more. This

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:19.670
causes

00:05:19.680 --> 00:05:22.790
you to move where before you probably would have

00:05:22.790 --> 00:05:22.800
been

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.710
comfortable in your surroundings.

00:05:24.710 --> 00:05:24.720
You

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:26.390
do

00:05:26.390 --> 00:05:26.400
not

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:29.150
really want to move out

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.950
because this is the way it

00:05:30.950 --> 00:05:30.960
has

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:33.290
always been—'Mom lived here, her mom lived

00:05:33.300 --> 00:05:36.050
here, and five

00:05:36.060 --> 00:05:37.790
generations of family have lived in this

00:05:39.409 --> 00:05:39.419
town.'It

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:42.890
takes pressure to make you want

00:05:42.900 --> 00:05:45.890
to move and do something. This

00:05:45.900 --> 00:05:48.770
relocating is uncomfortable,

00:05:48.770 --> 00:05:48.780
but

00:05:48.780 --> 00:05:50.150
it

00:05:50.150 --> 00:05:50.160
is

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:53.510
for what is coming in the near future,

00:05:53.520 --> 00:05:56.090
