believed in her heart and said out

00:21:06.289 --> 00:21:06.299
of

00:21:06.299 --> 00:21:08.330
her mouth. But God had another plan for

00:21:08.340 --> 00:21:09.770
her life.

00:21:09.780 --> 00:21:12.470
She had to take what she had and she had

00:21:12.480 --> 00:21:16.669
to sow it sacrificially to Elijah.

00:21:16.679 --> 00:21:21.049
In her sacrificial gift, God

00:21:21.059 --> 00:21:23.810
multiplied her

00:21:23.820 --> 00:21:25.669
because the Bible

00:21:25.679 --> 00:21:28.789
says there was a famine in the land. She

00:21:28.789 --> 00:21:28.799
is

00:21:28.799 --> 00:21:31.010
thinking, 'We are

00:21:31.010 --> 00:21:31.020
going to

00:21:31.020 --> 00:21:32.990
eat our last meal,

00:21:33.000 --> 00:21:35.390
our last wafer,

00:21:35.390 --> 00:21:35.400
and

00:21:35.400 --> 00:21:37.130
we

00:21:37.140 --> 00:21:39.230
are

00:21:39.230 --> 00:21:39.240
going

00:21:40.850 --> 00:21:40.860
to

00:21:40.860 --> 00:21:42.350
die,'but

00:21:42.360 --> 00:21:45.110
God had a bigger plan. What

00:21:45.110 --> 00:21:45.120
did

00:21:45.120 --> 00:21:49.669
she have to do? She sowed in famine and

00:21:49.679 --> 00:21:51.950
she reaped

00:21:51.960 --> 00:21:54.950
more than a hundredfold. She took all the

00:21:54.960 --> 00:21:57.169
oil and

00:21:57.179 --> 00:21:59.690
sold it, and the Bible says

00:21:59.700 --> 00:22:02.270
she had enough to basically

00:22:02.280 --> 00:22:06.289
get through all of the famine

00:22:06.299 --> 00:22:08.690
of what was going on around her. If

00:22:08.700 --> 00:22:10.190
God would do it for them in the Old

00:22:10.200 --> 00:22:11.930
Covenant,

00:22:11.930 --> 00:22:11.940
how

00:22:11.940 --> 00:22:14.690
much

00:22:14.700 --> 00:22:19.310
more will He do it for

00:22:19.320 --> 00:22:21.649
you? Obey and do

00:22:21.649 --> 00:22:21.659
what

00:22:21.659 --> 00:22:24.470
He

00:22:24.470 --> 00:22:24.480
has

00:22:24.480 --> 00:22:27.590
told you. God will

00:22:27.600 --> 00:22:30.590
extend and multiply your household. I

00:22:30.600 --> 00:22:32.930
have seen that what is coming

00:22:32.940 --> 00:22:35.210
is terrible for the people who do

00:22:35.210 --> 00:22:35.220
not

00:22:35.220 --> 00:22:37.070
listen to Him. If you are not listening

00:22:37.070 --> 00:22:37.080
and

00:22:37.080 --> 00:22:39.350
obeying, you are in trouble. So

00:22:39.350 --> 00:22:39.360
take

00:22:39.360 --> 00:22:41.930
that oil just like she did

00:22:41.930 --> 00:22:41.940
and

00:22:41.940 --> 00:22:43.430
sell

00:22:43.430 --> 00:22:43.440
it.

00:22:43.440 --> 00:22:46.250
In

00:22:46.260 --> 00:22:50.029
Genesis 26, Isaac sowed in

00:22:50.039 --> 00:22:52.370
famine. There was a

00:22:52.380 --> 00:22:55.070
famine in the land, and Isaac sowed in famine.

00:22:55.080 --> 00:22:57.470
In that famine,

00:22:57.480 --> 00:23:00.710
God blessed his crops and he reaped a

00:23:00.720 --> 00:23:03.590
hundredfold return in that same year. There

00:23:03.590 --> 00:23:03.600
is

00:23:03.600 --> 00:23:06.110
a miracle in

00:23:06.120 --> 00:23:07.010
itself.

00:23:07.020 --> 00:23:10.490
He obeyed in

00:23:10.490 --> 00:23:10.500
famine—in

00:23:10.500 --> 00:23:12.289
drought—but

00:23:12.299 --> 00:23:15.710
he sowed in famine

00:23:15.720 --> 00:23:19.610
and reaped a hundredfold that same

00:23:19.620 --> 00:23:20.990
year.

00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.930
Great harvest came to him, but what did he

00:23:23.940 --> 00:23:27.049
have to do? He had to sow the seed to

00:23:27.059 --> 00:23:29.510
reap the harvest. It did not just happen.

00:23:29.520 --> 00:23:31.490
He did not go to his mailbox

00:23:31.500 --> 00:23:33.649
every day and

00:23:33.659 --> 00:23:35.450
say, 'Did the

00:23:35.460 --> 00:23:38.149
blessing come?'He had to act in faith.

00:23:38.159 --> 00:23:42.289
Faith without works is dead.

00:23:42.299 --> 00:23:46.070
You have to be able to put

00:23:46.080 --> 00:23:48.830
your faith into motion

00:23:48.840 --> 00:23:51.110
to be able to reap

00:23:51.120 --> 00:23:53.210
out of the spirit realm because every

00:23:53.220 --> 00:23:55.789
seed produces after its own kind.

00:23:55.799 --> 00:23:58.850
When you are sowing into what

00:23:58.860 --> 00:24:01.250
God tells you to do, like

00:24:01.260 --> 00:24:04.549
ministries and

00:24:04.549 --> 00:24:04.559
helping

00:24:04.559 --> 00:24:06.169
people, maybe you

00:24:06.169 --> 00:24:06.179
are

00:24:06.179 --> 00:24:08.029
sowing a seed

00:24:08.039 --> 00:24:10.190
by buying a widow woman some food or

00:24:10.190 --> 00:24:10.200
paying

00:24:10.200 --> 00:24:12.230
her electric bill.

00:24:12.240 --> 00:24:13.789
Maybe she is living next door and you say,

00:24:13.799 --> 00:24:15.590
'Lord, put it on my heart to pay

00:24:15.590 --> 00:24:15.600
her

00:24:15.600 --> 00:24:17.450
electric bill.'You sow into good ground.

00:24:17.460 --> 00:24:19.010
Find good ground—that is what I am trying to

00:24:19.020 --> 00:24:20.690
tell you.

00:24:20.700 --> 00:24:23.750
The seeds that you planted

00:24:23.760 --> 00:24:27.289
today, you will reap. It is seed,

00:24:27.289 --> 00:24:27.299
time,

00:24:27.299 --> 00:24:29.090
harvest. There

00:24:29.090 --> 00:24:29.100
is

00:24:29.100 --> 00:24:31.310
a seed, there is time, and there

00:24:31.310 --> 00:24:31.320
is

00:24:31.320 --> 00:24:32.810
a harvest, just like it is in the field

00:24:32.810 --> 00:24:32.820
where

00:24:32.820 --> 00:24:36.049
you sow the corn and watch for the blade, the

00:24:36.059 --> 00:24:37.490
ear, and then the full

00:24:37.500 --> 00:24:40.250
manifestation.

00:24:40.260 --> 00:24:42.289
You have to realize that is the way

00:24:42.299 --> 00:24:44.090
the spirit realm operates, too. Do

00:24:44.090 --> 00:24:44.100
not

00:24:44.100 --> 00:24:45.710
be

00:24:45.720 --> 00:24:47.750
afraid about what is coming.

00:24:47.760 --> 00:24:51.409
You have the ability to sow a seed, and

00:24:51.419 --> 00:24:53.810
in that ability, you have

00:24:53.820 --> 00:24:56.210
the ability to receive a harvest.

00:24:56.220 --> 00:24:59.649
Look what He did for

00:24:59.659 --> 00:25:02.750
Isaac and Abraham in

00:25:02.760 --> 00:25:05.930
famine.

00:25:05.940 --> 00:25:07.610
There were famines in the land with Joseph—seven years

00:25:07.610 --> 00:25:07.620
of plenty and

00:25:07.620 --> 00:25:09.770
seven

00:25:09.780 --> 00:25:11.930
years of

00:25:11.940 --> 00:25:15.049
famine.

00:25:17.700 --> 00:25:20.270
Google famines in the Bible.

00:25:20.280 --> 00:25:22.909
Look at what God did for the people in

00:25:22.919 --> 00:25:24.830
the Bible when there was a famine. He

00:25:24.840 --> 00:25:26.570
always told them to sacrificially do

00:25:26.580 --> 00:25:29.390
something, but He always came through. Elijah

00:25:29.390 --> 00:25:29.400
was

00:25:29.400 --> 00:25:31.250
sitting on the

00:25:31.260 --> 00:25:33.169
side of the river and the raven brought

00:25:33.179 --> 00:25:35.029
him the meal. He did not have to worry

00:25:35.039 --> 00:25:37.370
about it every single day for a long

00:25:37.380 --> 00:25:39.110
time until He told him to

00:25:39.120 --> 00:25:41.269
move on. A raven brought him his

00:25:41.269 --> 00:25:41.279
meal—I

00:25:41.279 --> 00:25:42.710
believe it was

00:25:42.720 --> 00:25:45.049
twice a day,

00:25:45.059 --> 00:25:48.529
at noon and at dinner time.

00:25:48.539 --> 00:25:50.330
If you know ravens,

00:25:50.340 --> 00:25:53.210
ravens are dirty, nasty birds, but

00:25:55.799 --> 00:25:58.789
the Lord

00:25:58.799 --> 00:26:02.870
used that raven to bring

00:26:02.880 --> 00:26:06.409
Elijah the bread and took

00:26:06.419 --> 00:26:08.930
care of him for that whole season.

00:26:08.940 --> 00:26:12.110
God will do anything He can to take

00:26:12.120 --> 00:26:14.510
care of you for what is coming. Do not

00:26:14.520 --> 00:26:17.510
fear what is about to happen. Do

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:20.210
not fear any kind of financial crash. Do

00:26:20.220 --> 00:26:21.649
not fear

00:26:21.659 --> 00:26:23.690
not having enough groceries on the

00:26:23.700 --> 00:26:26.269
shelf. The Lord showed me people

00:26:26.279 --> 00:26:28.610
gathering around tables where their pots

00:26:28.620 --> 00:26:31.370
were empty and blessing the food, and

00:26:31.380 --> 00:26:33.470
the food coming into the pot

00:26:33.480 --> 00:26:36.610
supernaturally. We serve

00:26:36.610 --> 00:26:36.620
a

00:26:36.620 --> 00:26:39.529
supernatural God,

00:26:39.539 --> 00:26:42.350
and Jesus Christ is the same yesterday,

00:26:42.360 --> 00:26:45.289
today, and forever. If He can bless some

00:26:45.299 --> 00:26:48.169
pots on the marriage

00:26:48.169 --> 00:26:48.179
feast's

00:26:48.179 --> 00:26:50.570
first miracle... He was

00:26:50.580 --> 00:26:52.610
there for the

00:26:52.620 --> 00:26:54.470
celebration, and with the pots of water, He

00:26:54.480 --> 00:26:56.930
said, 'Go,'and Mary told them, 'Go

00:26:56.940 --> 00:26:59.330
and do whatever He tells you to

00:26:59.330 --> 00:26:59.340
do.'See,

00:26:59.340 --> 00:27:00.909
there it is again:

00:27:00.919 --> 00:27:04.610
obeying and sowing the seed.

00:27:04.620 --> 00:27:07.549
They went and filled

00:27:07.559 --> 00:27:10.850
the pots full of water, and Jesus

00:27:10.860 --> 00:27:13.310
blessed those pots, and there were

00:27:13.320 --> 00:27:15.110
hundreds and hundreds of gallons of

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:17.930
fresh new wine.

00:27:17.940 --> 00:27:20.930
It took them acting in

00:27:20.940 --> 00:27:23.330
obedience to what the Lord and Mary

00:27:23.340 --> 00:27:24.830
told them

00:27:24.830 --> 00:27:24.840
to do—sowing

00:27:24.840 --> 00:27:26.870
a seed

00:27:26.880 --> 00:27:27.970
by

00:27:27.980 --> 00:27:31.070
putting in the

00:27:31.070 --> 00:27:31.080
water—and

00:27:31.080 --> 00:27:32.390
then Jesus blessed it.

00:27:33.539 --> 00:27:36.769
But it takes an act. Faith is an

00:27:36.779 --> 00:27:37.490
act. It

00:27:37.490 --> 00:27:37.500
is

00:27:37.500 --> 00:27:40.970
not standing there

00:27:40.980 --> 00:27:42.950
and just waiting for something to happen;

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:45.950
you have to put your faith into motion

00:27:45.960 --> 00:27:47.750
for the manifestation of what you

00:27:47.750 --> 00:27:47.760
are

00:27:47.760 --> 00:27:50.330
believing for.

00:27:52.200 --> 00:27:55.070
If He

00:27:55.080 --> 00:27:56.930
tells you to put back silver, buy silver

00:27:56.940 --> 00:27:59.330
coins. If He tells you to buy a

00:27:59.330 --> 00:27:59.340
gun,

00:27:59.340 --> 00:28:01.730
do what He told you to do

00:28:01.740 --> 00:28:04.490
and the Lord will bless it.

00:28:04.500 --> 00:28:06.529
The Lord

00:28:06.539 --> 00:28:08.029
just told me, 'What are you believing for?'I

00:28:08.029 --> 00:28:08.039
will

00:28:08.039 --> 00:28:09.710
go back to that when I was mowing

00:28:09.720 --> 00:28:12.049
the grass. What are you believing for? Are

00:28:12.059 --> 00:28:13.789
you believing for the lack to happen to

00:28:13.799 --> 00:28:16.430
your house, Brandon?

00:28:16.440 --> 00:28:18.409
Because what you believe for

00:28:18.409 --> 00:28:18.419
is

00:28:18.419 --> 00:28:20.810
going to manifest. Once you

00:28:20.820 --> 00:28:22.190
start speaking it out of your mouth, that

00:28:22.190 --> 00:28:22.200
is

00:28:22.200 --> 00:28:23.630
going

00:28:23.630 --> 00:28:23.640
to

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:26.570
manifest. You have

00:28:26.580 --> 00:28:29.450
to learn how to believe in drought and

00:28:29.460 --> 00:28:31.250
famine.

00:28:38.039 --> 00:28:40.310
Renew your mind with the Word

00:28:40.320 --> 00:28:42.289
of God and what He said He would do for

00:28:42.299 --> 00:28:45.350
you, and meditate on that Word. Do not

00:28:45.360 --> 00:28:48.590
allow fear—even what I have told you is

00:28:48.600 --> 00:28:50.810
coming. That is not for fear;

00:28:50.810 --> 00:28:50.820
it

00:28:50.820 --> 00:28:52.430
is

00:28:52.430 --> 00:28:52.440
for

00:28:52.440 --> 00:28:55.610
preparation. I am a watchman on the wall. I

00:28:55.610 --> 00:28:55.620
am

00:28:55.620 --> 00:28:57.289
on the wall

00:28:57.299 --> 00:28:59.149
looking out

00:28:59.149 --> 00:28:59.159
and

00:28:59.159 --> 00:29:01.549
saying, 'A storm is

00:29:01.549 --> 00:29:01.559
coming!'and what do

00:29:01.559 --> 00:29:03.409
other people do?

00:29:03.409 --> 00:29:03.419
They

00:29:03.419 --> 00:29:04.549
get ready for

00:29:04.559 --> 00:29:07.190
the storm. We

00:29:07.200 --> 00:29:09.350
speak to the storms in our lives and

00:29:09.360 --> 00:29:11.810
cause them to dissipate. Jesus was able

00:29:11.820 --> 00:29:14.510
to speak to a great storm

00:29:14.510 --> 00:29:14.520
while

00:29:14.520 --> 00:29:16.490
He was asleep on the boat.

00:29:16.500 --> 00:29:19.190
He spoke, 'Peace, be still,'to the

00:29:19.200 --> 00:29:22.909
storm, and the waves and the seas were at

00:29:22.919 --> 00:29:26.769
peace. You have the same ability

00:29:26.779 --> 00:29:29.690
inside of you because Jesus dwells on

00:29:29.700 --> 00:29:31.610
the inside of you, and the Bible

00:29:31.610 --> 00:29:31.620
says

00:29:31.620 --> 00:29:34.370
Greater works will you do than Him.

00:29:34.380 --> 00:29:37.310
You have that same ability

00:29:37.320 --> 00:29:39.649
dwelling on the inside of you. The Holy

00:29:39.659 --> 00:29:42.950
Ghost dwells on the inside of you,

00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:45.529
and you have the same ability to do what

00:29:45.539 --> 00:29:46.549
He

00:29:46.549 --> 00:29:46.559
did—raise

00:29:46.559 --> 00:29:49.490
the dead, cast out devils, and heal the

00:29:49.500 --> 00:29:52.130
sick. It is all the Great Commission.

00:29:52.140 --> 00:29:54.289
But it never said we would

00:29:54.289 --> 00:29:54.299
have to suffer

00:29:54.299 --> 00:29:56.450
through famine.

00:29:56.460 --> 00:29:58.610
We may see the

00:29:58.610 --> 00:29:58.620
famine

00:29:58.620 --> 00:30:00.830
all around us,

00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:03.470
but I am not going to participate

00:30:03.480 --> 00:30:07.370
in it. I refuse to participate in the

00:30:07.380 --> 00:30:10.430
financial crash. I refuse to participate

00:30:10.440 --> 00:30:13.730
in the Great Depression. I will not live

00:30:13.740 --> 00:30:17.090
that with my children. In my house, we

00:30:17.100 --> 00:30:19.549
will have more than enough because I am a

00:30:19.559 --> 00:30:22.730
tither, a giver, a sower, and a

00:30:22.740 --> 00:30:25.190
believer. I

00:30:25.190 --> 00:30:25.200
am

00:30:25.200 --> 00:30:27.289
not a doubter. Say it out

00:30:27.289 --> 00:30:27.299
of

00:30:27.299 --> 00:30:28.850
your mouth: 'I am a believer, I am not a

00:30:28.860 --> 00:30:31.310
doubter. What God did for them, He will do

00:30:31.320 --> 00:30:34.190
for me.'He is no respecter of persons; if

00:30:34.200 --> 00:30:36.409
He took care of them, He will take care of

00:30:36.419 --> 00:30:38.210
me. That is what He wanted me to tell

00:30:38.220 --> 00:30:41.149
you today. Believe for the

00:30:41.159 --> 00:30:43.730
impossible.

00:30:46.500 --> 00:30:47.930
It may look like it

00:30:47.930 --> 00:30:47.940
is

00:30:47.940 --> 00:30:49.549
not going to happen—like that

00:30:49.549 --> 00:30:49.559
lady who thought

00:30:49.559 --> 00:30:51.409
she

00:30:51.409 --> 00:30:51.419
would

00:30:51.419 --> 00:30:53.330
cook her last meal

00:30:53.340 --> 00:30:55.610
and die. What a bleak

00:30:55.620 --> 00:30:58.730
way to think, yet God had a plan.

00:30:58.740 --> 00:31:01.070
God has a plan for you. How much more

00:31:01.080 --> 00:31:02.930
does God love you? That

00:31:02.930 --> 00:31:02.940
is

00:31:02.940 --> 00:31:04.789
what I have for you today. I hope

00:31:04.799 --> 00:31:06.409
this blessed you. Now I am going to pray

00:31:06.419 --> 00:31:08.090
for you and give you

00:31:08.100 --> 00:31:09.889
some encouragement because God has

00:31:09.899 --> 00:31:12.350
a plan for you and He loves you.

00:31:12.360 --> 00:31:14.570
He is more than able to do

00:31:14.580 --> 00:31:16.370
exceedingly abundantly above all that

00:31:16.380 --> 00:31:17.990
you dare ask or think according to the

00:31:18.000 --> 00:31:19.370
power that is working through you.

00:31:19.380 --> 00:31:22.190
You have to understand Jesus is

00:31:22.200 --> 00:31:24.350
going to use you, but

00:31:24.360 --> 00:31:26.570
you have to be listening to Him. Listen

00:31:26.580 --> 00:31:28.610
to Him today.

00:31:28.620 --> 00:31:30.409
Many of you say, 'I do not hear Him at all.'I

00:31:30.409 --> 00:31:30.419
do not

00:31:30.419 --> 00:31:32.269
believe that.

00:31:32.279 --> 00:31:35.029
Get silent.

00:31:35.039 --> 00:31:37.190
Get quiet.

00:31:37.190 --> 00:31:37.200
In

00:31:37.200 --> 00:31:38.950
that still, small voice, He will talk to you.

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:41.810
Meditate on His Word, read

00:31:41.810 --> 00:31:41.820
it,

00:31:41.820 --> 00:31:44.510
and

00:31:44.520 --> 00:31:48.409
pray. Father, I love You. You said Your

00:31:48.419 --> 00:31:50.149
sheep will know Your voice and a

00:31:50.159 --> 00:31:52.549
stranger's voice they will not follow. I

00:31:52.559 --> 00:31:54.470
will not follow any kind of demonic

00:31:54.480 --> 00:31:56.930
spirit. I will not have a familiar spirit

00:31:56.940 --> 00:32:00.409
coming in and messing with my ears. I

00:32:00.419 --> 00:32:02.450
will hear You, Lord, and I will follow

00:32:02.460 --> 00:32:04.970
Your voice concerning my life. I

00:32:04.980 --> 00:32:06.529
thank You, Father, that You are going to

00:32:06.539 --> 00:32:10.190
speak to me today. I believe by faith—say this: 'I believe by faith

